commentable_entity.ask: Amber Heard DOES NOT speak for me! Victims of DA & SA SPEAK OUT!
commentable_entity.title: Amber Heard DOES NOT speak for me! Victims of DA & SA SPEAK OUT!
commentable_entity.description:
Through watching the Johnny Depp, Amber Heard trial, we all saw 'her evidence' of violent sexual attacks and brutal beatings she said she constantly received. Yet, the evidence was clear that she herself was the abusive person in the relationship. She had NO hospital admissions. NO real photographic images. Yet she stated to have 2 broken noses, bruising everywhere and constant pummeling. In her words, "Johnny always wore his rings". 

I am a SA and DA survivor. I heard her taunting him in those tapes. I saw the images of JD after she'd viciously attacked him. I heard her admit on tape to beating him several times. I heard her challenge him to tell the world that he was a victim of domestic assault & she said nobody would believe him. 

Johnny. We believe you. We're sorry it took so long.
commentable_entity.letter_body: Amber Heard DOES NOT speak for me! Victims of DA & SA SPEAK OUT!
